{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01P3k7AudtSexXUCfRJJQy7F","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All three verification criteria pass:\n\n1. **Cluster health: green** — all 4 primary shards have 2 replicas each, 0 unassigned shards.\n2. **All 3 nodes present** — `es-cluster-0` (master), `es-cluster-1`, and `es-cluster-2` all appear in `/_cat/nodes`.\n3. **`app-data` readable** — index returns the seed document successfully.\n\n**Root cause:** An external process corrupted the `es-config` ConfigMap by replacing the correct `discovery.seed_hosts` entries (`es-cluster-{0,1,2}.es-cluster`) with invalid hostnames (`invalid-host-{1,2,3}`). Without valid seed hosts the pods couldn't discover each other and the cluster couldn't re-form after the restart.\n\n**Fix applied:** Restored `discovery.seed_hosts` to the original headless-service DNS names from the ConfigMap annotation, then waited for the StatefulSet pods to cycle and come up with the corrected config."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":340,"cache_read_input_tokens":33902,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":340},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"f01ce2a3-9eab-4c36-9844-b5111fed512e","uuid":"38548074-736e-476c-bc6e-4dcebd1ce2cc","request_id":"req_011CceppyUssq3AH3pjGJXPr"}
